🧠 How It Works
Text Preprocessing — Cleans and tokenizes input text
Dual Analysis Engine:
VADER (Valence Aware Dictionary) — Rule-based, great for social media
TextBlob — ML-based pattern analysis
Ensemble Scoring — Combines both engines for higher accuracy
Classification — Maps scores to Positive/Negative/Neutral with confidence
